title: #92Noon! Vox Quarantined in the Box
description: PA & Nordo are all by themselves in the box today, in the wake of the cancellation of morning skate, and quite possibly the game tonight against the Vegas Golden Knights due to increasing fears of Corona Virus. A surprise drop in from goalie, Alex Stalock, on what's been going on down in the locker room. Michael Russo joins over the Opal to discuss the possible cancellation of the NHL season. FSN's Ryan Carter and the Vikings Adam Thielen join as well.
